SenStore::Transducer

Overview

interface Transducer

Operation Index

getFields
Gets the fields of this Transducer object.
setFields
Updates the fields of this Transducer object.

Operations

TransducerFields getFields()

Gets the fields of this Transducer object.

Return Value

Transducer object fields

void setFields(TransducerFields fields, FieldNameList fieldNames)

Updates the fields of this Transducer object. If one or more fields are specified, only the fields listed will be updated, the other fields will be left unchanged. If the field list is empty ALL fields will be updated. The available fields are:

  • Model
  • Identifier

Parameters

fields
updated fields structure
fieldNames
a string list with field names to be updated
